_sText:
A whole new hoejhus map! Created from start with a totally new look!

SPECIAL DIFFERENCES:

- The texture is more smooth
- When you plant the bomb, the room gets red
- Special adds in the tunnels
- An awesome t-roof
- A very usefull ladder between, underground, 1. floor, 2. floor and ct-roof
- Metal bridge aka. stone bridge, goes to 1. floor and underground
- There isn't a tiny crack in the bottom of t-spawn (The place where you could crouch and shoot the people in the end of the tunnel)
